verbose_text: There was no clear relationship between serum Lz levels and markers of HPG axis activity, since Lz levels measured at 3 months did not correlate with the changes (0-3 months) in serum T, estradiol, T/estradiol ratio, iB, LH, FSH, or AMH levels or with the change in testicular volume (in all, P = NS) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
